1
00:00:22,620 --> 00:00:28,450
♪Hari kemarin yang tampak kabur,
perlahan muncul di pikiranku♪

2
00:00:29,410 --> 00:00:35,950
♪Bagai pertemuan yang ditakdirkan,
agar kita sama-sama berjuang♪

3
00:00:36,250 --> 00:00:42,750
♪Masa lalu hilang mengikuti awan,
ingatan tertinggal jelas di hati♪

4
00:00:43,580 --> 00:00:50,250
♪Semua yang dirasakan bersama,
bagai tahun yang indah♪

5
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:57,450
♪Jalan penuh bahaya dan rintangan,
begitu banyak orang dan perubahan♪

6
00:00:57,910 --> 00:01:05,330
♪Musnahkan halangan dan terus maju,
siapa yang lebih hebat dariku♪

7
00:01:06,790 --> 00:01:13,790
♪Langit mulai gelap dan dingin,
semua kembali ke asalnya♪

8
00:01:13,790 --> 00:01:20,750
♪Menerjang semua kesulitan,
dan berdiri di puncak tertinggi♪

9
00:01:20,750 --> 00:01:27,790
♪Melihat pemandangan
yang seindah tulisan puisi♪

10
00:01:27,790 --> 00:01:31,160
♪Bersama-sama menyeberangi sungai
dan melewati perjalanan panjang♪

11
00:01:31,660 --> 00:01:35,950
♪Biarkan keberanian kita
meninggalkan nama baik di dunia♪

12
00:01:35,950 --> 00:01:39,870
=Dunia Douluo=

13
00:01:40,080 --> 00:01:42,870
=Episode 29=

14
00:01:46,760 --> 00:01:50,190
Kuberi tahu kebenarannya,
bukan agar kau membalas dendam.

15
00:01:51,270 --> 00:01:55,720
Sebaliknya, aku harap di hatimu
tak ada dendam.

16
00:01:56,270 --> 00:01:59,080
Kau punya misi
dan jalan yang harus kau lalui.

17
00:01:59,310 --> 00:02:02,680
Jangan sampai dendam
menutup matamu.

18
00:02:03,040 --> 00:02:04,910
Menghancurkan hidupmu.

19
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:10,440
Namun, semua orang Balai Roh
Pelindung yang membunuh ibuku,…

20
00:02:12,230 --> 00:02:13,870
…satu pun tak akan kulepaskan.

21
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:16,960
Guru.

22
00:02:17,470 --> 00:02:20,380
Masalah ayah-ibuku di waktu itu,
apa masih ada yang tidak kuketahui?

23
00:02:20,440 --> 00:02:22,830
Kalau kau tahu, mohon beri tahu aku.

24
00:02:22,890 --> 00:02:25,560
Sebenarnya, ada beberapa hal yang
lebih baik tak kau ketahui.

25
00:02:25,720 --> 00:02:27,190
Paling tidak, kau tak akan menderita.

26
00:02:28,670 --> 00:02:30,750
Guru, kau pernah berkata padaku.

27
00:02:31,190 --> 00:02:33,000
'Penderitaan' sangat suka orang kuat,…

28
00:02:33,750 --> 00:02:35,440
…karena saat kita menderita,…

29
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:37,630
…baru kita kenali diri
kita yang sebenarnya.

30
00:02:39,390 --> 00:02:42,540
Tak peduli apa hasilnya,
aku tak akan jalan di kegelapan.

31
00:02:42,600 --> 00:02:43,420
Tak akan dijatuhkan.

32
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,960
Guru, aku sungguh telah siap.

33
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:50,470
Tolong beri tahu aku.

34
00:02:54,030 --> 00:02:54,600
Baiklah.

35
00:02:55,670 --> 00:02:57,800
Ayahmu dulu adalah
orang kepercayaan Qian Xunji.

36
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,470
Salah satu orang terkuat di dunia.

37
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,270
Juga idolaku dahulu.

38
00:03:03,600 --> 00:03:05,600
Dahulu setelah Segitiga
Besi Emas kami bubar,…

39
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:07,960
…aku ikuti langkah ayahmu.

40
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:10,660
Bergabung ke Balai Roh Pelindung.

41
00:03:11,110 --> 00:03:12,720
Fokus meneliti roh pelindung
mutasi.

42
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:18,190
Jadi, saat Xiao Wu kena racun
Bu Le di Akademi Shi Lanke…

43
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:21,160
…kau berkata ingin pergi ke Balai
Pelindung Roh untuk minta obatnya?

44
00:03:21,830 --> 00:03:23,820
Kalau besok dia masih
belum datang, bagaimana?

45
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,010
Racun di tubuh Xiao Wu
tak akan tahan selama itu.

46
00:03:27,190 --> 00:03:28,800
Kalau tiga hari lagi tak muncul,…

47
00:03:32,480 --> 00:03:34,080
…maka aku pergi
ke Balai Roh Pelindung.

48
00:03:34,830 --> 00:03:35,670
Balai Roh Pelindung?

49
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:37,600
Untuk apa kau ke sana?

50
00:03:39,320 --> 00:03:41,080
Jangan banyak tanya.
Aku ada cara sendiri.

51
00:03:41,470 --> 00:03:42,030
Benar.

52
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:44,440
Inti penelitian
roh pelindung mutasi…

53
00:03:44,830 --> 00:03:46,550
…kulakukan saat
di Balai Roh Pelindung.

54
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:49,870
Kemudian, ayahmu keluar
dari Balai Roh Pelindung.

55
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:52,630
Diburon oleh Qian Xunji.

56
00:03:53,750 --> 00:03:54,630
Ayahmu kalah perang.

57
00:03:55,910 --> 00:03:57,390
Sejak saat itu, tak lagi ada kabar.

58
00:03:57,670 --> 00:03:59,320
Aku pun tinggalkan
Balai Roh Pelindung.

59
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:02,310
Penelitian roh pelindung mutasi
pun berhenti di sana.

60
00:04:02,600 --> 00:04:04,600
Detail di antaranya,
serta perihal ibumu…

61
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,360
…adalah rahasia Balai Roh Pelindung.

62
00:04:07,110 --> 00:04:08,060
Kemudian?

63
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:11,470
Setelah Qian Xunji mati, istrinya,
Bibi Dong, teruskan posisinya.

64
00:04:12,270 --> 00:04:14,670
Hal menyangkut Balai Roh Pelindung
tak lagi kuikuti.

65
00:04:15,110 --> 00:04:17,720
Sampai di Desa Api Malam,
muncul obat roh pelindung mutasi.

66
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:20,050
Aku curiga,
dalang di belakang Ye Zhiqiu…

67
00:04:20,050 --> 00:04:21,720
…ada hubungan dengan
Balai Roh Pelindung.

68
00:04:22,190 --> 00:04:24,470
Namun, saat kuketahui Hu Liena
juga sedang menyelidiki…

69
00:04:24,470 --> 00:04:25,910
…obat bagi roh pelindung mutasi,…

70
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,320
…aku hapuskan kecurigaanku.

71
00:04:30,950 --> 00:04:31,600
Guru.

72
00:04:32,720 --> 00:04:36,480
Aku sekarang bisa pastikan, dalang
di balik roh pelindung mutasi…

73
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:37,790
…adalah ayahku.

74
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,550
Pertama.

75
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,880
Dia dulu bagian Balai Roh Pelindung.

76
00:04:44,390 --> 00:04:46,780
Ada kesempatan tahu penelitian
obat roh pelindung mutasi.

77
00:04:47,110 --> 00:04:47,510
Kedua.

78
00:04:48,670 --> 00:04:49,950
Demi balaskan dendam ibuku,…

79
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,570
…dia bermusuhan dengan
Balai Roh Pelindung.

80
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:54,390
Ditambah dengan ucapan Ye Zhiqiu,…

81
00:04:55,110 --> 00:04:57,720
…Master Hao Tian gunakan
obat roh pelindung mutasi…

82
00:04:58,200 --> 00:05:00,940
…untuk kendalikan banyak master roh,
menjadikan mereka bawahannya.

83
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:03,040
Kalau semua master roh
pelindung mutasi…

84
00:05:03,160 --> 00:05:04,840
…berkumpul melawan
Balai Roh Pelindung,…

85
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:07,300
…maka akhirnya
tak bisa terbayangkan.

86
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:09,320
Lalu, apa rencanamu?

87
00:05:10,760 --> 00:05:12,230
Masuk final, hentikan dia.

88
00:05:12,790 --> 00:05:13,480
Lalu?

89
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,550
Lalu, beri tahu dia.

90
00:05:15,320 --> 00:05:16,640
Kita tak akan lupakan dendam.

91
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,950
Namun, tak boleh lukai
orang tak bersalah.

92
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:20,700
Aku ingin sadarkan dia.

93
00:05:21,040 --> 00:05:23,010
Tak boleh serang
seluruh Balai Roh Pelindung.

94
00:05:23,500 --> 00:05:26,000
Aku akan usahakan yang terbaik
membantumu masuk final.

95
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,000
Biarkan seluruh Dunia
Douluo tahu kehebatanmu.

96
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:28,550
Tidak.

97
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:32,000
Harusnya, biarkan seluruh Dunia
Douluo tahu kehebatan Shi Lanke.

98
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:44,950
Xiao Wu.

99
00:05:45,760 --> 00:05:47,320
Mau makan bersama kami?

100
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:49,160
Tidak, tidak perlu.

101
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:52,640
Apa jangan-jangan,
Kak San tidak persiapkan dirimu?

102
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,350
Aku ada ini.

103
00:05:56,670 --> 00:05:58,110
Tanaman obat bermutu apa ini?

104
00:05:58,880 --> 00:06:01,440
Kata Tang San, ini adalah
Tanaman Patah Hati.

105
00:06:01,790 --> 00:06:03,600
Lalu, kau tak makan?

106
00:06:08,000 --> 00:06:08,790
Xiao Wu?

107
00:06:11,440 --> 00:06:12,270
Xiao Wu.

108
00:06:13,200 --> 00:06:14,640
Dari tadi, kau selalu tak fokus.

109
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,550
Kenapa? Ada masalah?

110
00:06:19,110 --> 00:06:21,110
Dugu Yan bilang dia suka Tang San.

111
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,110
Lalu?

112
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,880
Dia bercanda.

113
00:06:31,760 --> 00:06:32,510
Baguslah.

114
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:35,350
Namun, aku rasa diriku aneh.

115
00:06:35,670 --> 00:06:36,640
Aneh bagaimana?

116
00:06:37,350 --> 00:06:38,390
Aku sangat khawatir.

117
00:06:38,640 --> 00:06:40,450
Sangat tak bersedia
Dugu Yan suka Tang San.

118
00:06:40,510 --> 00:06:41,670
Otakku kacau.

119
00:06:42,070 --> 00:06:43,070
Tak tahu kenapa?

120
00:06:43,550 --> 00:06:44,880
Masih tak tahu kenapa?

121
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:46,480
Gadis bodoh.

122
00:06:47,110 --> 00:06:49,000
Bukankah karena kau suka Tang San?

123
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,510
Suka?

124
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,790
Namun, aku hanya menganggapnya
sebagai kakak.

125
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:56,510
Sungguh anggap Kakak atau tidak,
coba saja juga akan tahu.

126
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:58,510
Coba bagaimana?

127
00:06:58,510 --> 00:07:00,200
Cium dia, pasti langsung tahu…

128
00:07:00,200 --> 00:07:02,030
…sebenarnya perasaanmu
padanya bagaimana.

129
00:07:03,600 --> 00:07:04,320
Sungguh?

130
00:07:06,320 --> 00:07:07,230
Aku rasa…

131
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,720
…sebenarnya, cara ini
sedikit berlebihan.

132
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:13,110
Namun, efeknya harusnya cukup baik.

133
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,390
Lalu, bagaimana
kau dan Kak Dai berciuman?

134
00:07:19,510 --> 00:07:20,390
Ciuman?

135
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,040
Kau dan Dai Mubai?

136
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:24,830
-Kapan ini terjadi?
-Tak pernah.

137
00:07:24,830 --> 00:07:26,820
Kami sama sekali tak pernah
bertemu sebelumnya.

138
00:07:26,820 --> 00:07:27,870
Hanya karena perjodohan.

139
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,510
Perjodohan?

140
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,510
Minggir kau.

141
00:07:32,320 --> 00:07:33,110
Kau jangan pergi.

142
00:07:33,110 --> 00:07:34,910
Cepat beri tahu aku,
bagaimana bisa begitu?!

143
00:07:34,910 --> 00:07:35,390
Pergi.

144
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,920
Kak Qing yang baik.

145
00:07:36,920 --> 00:07:37,920
Cepat beri tahu aku.

146
00:07:37,920 --> 00:07:39,390
Jangan begitu pelit.

147
00:07:40,070 --> 00:07:41,510
Aku berikan tanaman obatku padamu.

148
00:07:41,790 --> 00:07:42,580
Aku tak mau. Tak mau.

149
00:07:43,070 --> 00:07:45,480
Dengan menciumnya saja
sudah tak masalah?

150
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,510
Kak Qing.

151
00:07:48,510 --> 00:07:49,640
Jangan buat aku kesal. Pergi!

152
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:50,480
Beri tahu aku.

153
00:08:04,670 --> 00:08:05,920
Guru, bagaimana?

154
00:08:06,670 --> 00:08:08,820
Jamur Ungu Tingkat Sembilan
tingkatkan batasanku.

155
00:08:09,230 --> 00:08:12,230
Tang San, aku rasa, aku akhirnya
bisa dapatkan cincin roh ke-3ku.

156
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,830
Selamat, Guru.

157
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:16,950
Setelah kau tembus cincin roh ke-3,
pasti bisa capai lebih jauh.

158
00:08:18,600 --> 00:08:20,260
Tak penting apa
aku bisa naik atau tidak.

159
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,480
Kalian barulah harapanku.

160
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,720
Terima kasih, Guru.

161
00:08:25,510 --> 00:08:26,950
Hubungan guru-murid lumayan juga.

162
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:28,350
Senior.

163
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,670
Kapan Anda datang?

164
00:08:29,670 --> 00:08:30,390
Baru saja.

165
00:08:30,790 --> 00:08:31,270
Mari, duduk.

166
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:39,200
Senior. Anda tak pakai
liontin giokmu lagi?

167
00:08:39,200 --> 00:08:40,350
Sudah kulepaskan.

168
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:41,860
Tak perlu pakai lagi.

169
00:08:42,400 --> 00:08:43,330
Racun sudah terobati?

170
00:08:45,470 --> 00:08:49,350
Kali ini, aku berutang
satu hal padamu.

171
00:08:50,200 --> 00:08:53,590
Nanti, kalian ikut lomba,
kubantu atur musuhmu.

172
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:56,520
Kujamin kalian tak perlu bertarung,
langsung ke final.

173
00:08:58,760 --> 00:08:59,230
Ini…

174
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:06,840
Tentu, keluarga kerajaan Tiandou
tak mudah kuhadapi.

175
00:09:08,280 --> 00:09:09,030
Senior.

176
00:09:09,960 --> 00:09:11,320
Bukankah trikmu ini trik gelap?

177
00:09:11,550 --> 00:09:13,350
Apa kau harus katakan
seterus-terang itu?

178
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:14,760
Jangan, jangan, Senior.

179
00:09:15,150 --> 00:09:16,440
Jangan begitu.

180
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:21,670
Kalau ada yang ingin menjebak kami,
maka kau lindungi kami saja.

181
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:24,670
Jangan sampai kau lakukan hal lain.

182
00:09:25,110 --> 00:09:27,440
Kalau kalian kalah lomba,
jangan salahkan aku.

183
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:28,760
Tentu saja.

184
00:09:28,790 --> 00:09:29,550
Kompetisi adil.

185
00:09:29,640 --> 00:09:31,200
Siapa kalah dan menang,
bisa diterima.

186
00:09:31,400 --> 00:09:32,790
Bukankah kau ingin masuk final?

187
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,880
Itu juga harus andalkan
kekuatan sendiri baru bisa.

188
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,760
Tidakkah bocah ini sedikit bodoh?

189
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,970
Ada jalan pintas, tak mau ambil.

190
00:09:43,880 --> 00:09:45,400
Beruntung kau bukan cucu menantuku.

191
00:09:49,150 --> 00:09:49,710
Baiklah.

192
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:52,590
Aku pergi ke Akademi Canghui dulu.

193
00:09:52,640 --> 00:09:53,200
Ingin ikut?

194
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:54,960
Untuk apa kau ke sana?

195
00:09:54,960 --> 00:09:55,640
Balas dendam.

196
00:09:56,550 --> 00:09:59,960
Sekelompok bocah itu berani
racuni aku dan cucuku.

197
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,960
Senior, kau dengar aku.

198
00:10:02,000 --> 00:10:04,000
Aku baru saja ingin bicarakan
hal ini denganmu.

199
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:06,320
Bisakah kau jangan
pergi balas dendam dulu?

200
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,790
Lalu, liontin giok itu…

201
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:10,000
…merepotkanmu untuk
memakainya lagi.

202
00:10:10,550 --> 00:10:11,230
Kenapa?

203
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:14,710
Mengenai racunmu yang telah dibuang,
jangan kita sebarkan dulu.

204
00:10:14,780 --> 00:10:16,790
Aku khawatir setelah Canghui
tahu kau terobati,…

205
00:10:16,790 --> 00:10:17,960
…mereka akan coba cara lain.

206
00:10:18,350 --> 00:10:20,080
Lebih baik, kita tunggu dulu.

207
00:10:20,350 --> 00:10:23,320
Lihat apa yang Canghui ingin
kau lakukan dengan hal ini.

208
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:26,550
Kau kenal Master Dunia Douluo
di belakang mereka, 'kan?

209
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:28,350
Tanya langsung padanya saja.

210
00:10:29,470 --> 00:10:30,670
Aku tak bisa temui dia.

211
00:10:31,030 --> 00:10:33,720
Namun, aku sangat ingin tahu. Apa
sebenarnya yang ingin dia lakukan?

212
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:35,200
Aku akan kerja sama.

213
00:10:36,030 --> 00:10:36,990
Terima kasih, Senior.

214
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:38,080
Oh, ya.

215
00:10:38,670 --> 00:10:40,960
Tanaman obat bermutu itu,
apa kau masih perlu?

216
00:10:41,200 --> 00:10:43,840
Cincin roh ke-6 dan di atasnya
tak bisa gunakan benda itu lagi.

217
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:48,000
Pada akhirnya, master roh harus
andalkan kerja keras sendiri.

218
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:50,760
Ucapan Senior benar.

219
00:10:50,880 --> 00:10:51,640
Kau harus ingat.

220
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:52,880
Tentu.

221
00:10:53,550 --> 00:10:55,710
Masuk ke keluarga kerajaan Tiandou…

222
00:10:56,150 --> 00:10:58,000
…berarti sumber daya
datang lebih cepat.

223
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,180
Hal ini boleh tak diingat.

224
00:11:01,710 --> 00:11:03,910
Kudengar besok pendaftaran
akan segera ditutup.

225
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:06,590
Sebaiknya, kalian segera mendaftar
baru bicarakan lagi.

226
00:11:07,520 --> 00:11:08,150
Senior tenang.

227
00:11:08,670 --> 00:11:10,000
Bila tanaman obat itu dijual,…

228
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:12,100
…bukan hal sulit untuk dapatkan
2.000 lebih koin emas.

229
00:11:12,100 --> 00:11:12,520
Baik.

230
00:11:12,840 --> 00:11:13,520
Aku pergi dulu.

231
00:11:15,350 --> 00:11:16,080
Racun Kecil.

232
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:18,550
Kalau ada apa-apa, ke gua cari aku, ya.

233
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,520
Racun… Racun Kecil?

234
00:11:21,590 --> 00:11:24,150
Segala racun tak berguna,
menggunakan senjata tersembunyi.

235
00:11:24,910 --> 00:11:26,590
Kalau bukan kamu,
siapa lagi Racun Kecil?

236
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:30,710
Pergi dulu.

237
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,230
Senior, hati-hati.

238
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:50,810
Terima kasih.

239
00:11:54,910 --> 00:11:58,320
Master bilang sudah
tembus cincin roh ke-3?

240
00:12:02,030 --> 00:12:03,710
Kak Qing dan Rongrong bilang…

241
00:12:03,910 --> 00:12:05,960
…kekuatan roh sudah penuh,
sudah bisa naik tingkat.

242
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:07,990
Bagus sekali kalau begitu!

243
00:12:08,110 --> 00:12:10,670
Kekuatan akademi kita
bisa meningkat lagi!

244
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:23,400
Kenapa?

245
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,080
Wajahku kotor?

246
00:12:25,840 --> 00:12:27,710
Kau sudah cuci muka?

247
00:12:28,350 --> 00:12:29,400
Sudah cuci tadi pagi.

248
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:32,710
Sekarang sudah malam.

249
00:12:33,030 --> 00:12:36,110
Kalau tidak, kau lap mulutmu lagi.

250
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:39,150
Lap mulut?

251
00:12:48,150 --> 00:12:49,000
Sudah lap.

252
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:50,760
Lap lagi dengan lebih bersih.

253
00:12:51,110 --> 00:12:51,790
Lap lagi.

254
00:12:52,400 --> 00:12:54,320
Kenapa? Ada yang kotor?

255
00:13:09,230 --> 00:13:09,840
Kak San.

256
00:13:10,550 --> 00:13:11,110
Kak San.

257
00:13:11,960 --> 00:13:12,550
Hongjun.

258
00:13:13,000 --> 00:13:14,600
Kekuatan rohku dan Ou Sike
sudah penuh.

259
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:17,150
Kak Dai juga bisa naik ke cincin
roh ke-4. Meningkat keseluruhan.

260
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,150
Bagus sekali!

261
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:19,790
Kak Xiao Wu.

262
00:13:20,420 --> 00:13:21,200
Kenapa kau di sini?

263
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,300
Dia suruh aku lap mulut.

264
00:13:22,440 --> 00:13:23,150
Lap mulut?

265
00:13:23,520 --> 00:13:24,330
Untuk apa lap mulut?

266
00:13:24,790 --> 00:13:25,910
Aku juga tak jelas.

267
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:28,240
Kalau begitu, aku lapor hal ini
ke Kepala Akademi dulu.

268
00:13:28,280 --> 00:13:28,960
Kau pergi dulu.

269
00:14:06,550 --> 00:14:08,350
Tang San. Tang San.

270
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:13,670
Kepala Akademi?

271
00:14:28,840 --> 00:14:30,080
Kekuatan roh sudah penuh.

272
00:14:30,550 --> 00:14:31,760
Kenapa masih tak tenang?

273
00:14:32,180 --> 00:14:34,230
Tak perlu pedulikan
kekuatan roh atau apa pun itu.

274
00:14:34,230 --> 00:14:37,320
Kak Qing, menurutmu,
bagaimana dengan Xiao Wu?

275
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:39,440
Harusnya bisa, 'kan?

276
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,110
Kita pergi lihat saja.

277
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:45,590
Lihat?

278
00:14:47,840 --> 00:14:48,400
Tak boleh.

279
00:14:49,350 --> 00:14:50,710
Kak Qing.

280
00:14:51,030 --> 00:14:52,000
Tak pantas.

281
00:14:52,110 --> 00:14:53,200
Tak apa.

282
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:53,550
Begini.

283
00:14:53,550 --> 00:14:56,410
Aku gunakan Pagoda Cahaya Qibao-ku
untuk tambahkan kecepatan kita.

284
00:14:56,410 --> 00:14:58,230
Kalau ketahuan,
kita langsung pergi.

285
00:15:17,960 --> 00:15:18,880
Kak Qing.

286
00:15:19,760 --> 00:15:23,470
Kau lihat apa pagodaku ini
sedikit berbeda?

287
00:15:24,400 --> 00:15:27,440
Pagoda Cahaya Qibao
masih bisa berubah bentuk?

288
00:15:28,110 --> 00:15:30,880
Tak tahu. Aku juga tak pernah lihat
ia berubah jadi begini.

289
00:15:31,550 --> 00:15:33,320
Tidak mungkin rusak, 'kan?

290
00:15:33,520 --> 00:15:34,200
Cepat coba.

291
00:15:35,030 --> 00:15:36,840
Tambah kekuatan, tambah kecepatan!

292
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:40,790
Bagus, bagus.

293
00:15:40,790 --> 00:15:41,350
Tak rusak.

294
00:15:41,910 --> 00:15:44,000
Ayo, pergi. Cepat pergi lihat
Tang San dan Xiao Wu.

295
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:44,670
Tak boleh.

296
00:15:45,230 --> 00:15:45,940
Tak boleh pergi.

297
00:15:46,080 --> 00:15:48,470
Ayolah, kau pergi tidak?

298
00:15:48,670 --> 00:15:50,000
Kau tak pergi, aku pergi sendiri.

299
00:15:51,840 --> 00:15:52,590
Aku pergi.

300
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:05,790
Aku pergi perhatikan Rongrong.

301
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:08,170
Bukan karena keinginan sendiri.

302
00:16:11,150 --> 00:16:13,020
Tanaman obat bermutu
tak bisa dijual?

303
00:16:13,280 --> 00:16:14,280
Bukan tak bisa dijual.

304
00:16:14,440 --> 00:16:16,890
Melainkan semua orang bilang dua
hari lagi baru transaksi.

305
00:16:16,890 --> 00:16:18,590
Namun, besok hari akhir pendaftaran.

306
00:16:19,150 --> 00:16:21,710
Aku tanya orang-orang terdekatku.
Ini niat Bangsawan Xue Xing.

307
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:23,030
Sengaja menunda dua hari.

308
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:24,840
Kalau begitu, tak bisa daftar.

309
00:16:27,440 --> 00:16:28,030
Jangan panik.

310
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:29,640
Kita pikirkan cara lain.

311
00:16:30,150 --> 00:16:31,200
Kalau memang tak ada cara,…

312
00:16:31,320 --> 00:16:33,710
…maka kita hanya bisa cari
Putra Mahkota Xue Qinghe.

313
00:16:34,030 --> 00:16:36,910
Namun, kata Yu Tianheng, belakangan,
Pangeran Mahkota tak temui orang.

314
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,550
Bagaimanapun juga, harus dicoba.

315
00:16:40,030 --> 00:16:40,760
Tak apa.

316
00:16:41,350 --> 00:16:42,910
Bos Lan, kita pergi sekarang.

317
00:16:43,520 --> 00:16:44,000
Xiaogang.

318
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,860
Kau baru gunakan
Jamur Ungu Tingkat Sembilan.

319
00:16:45,860 --> 00:16:47,750
Jangan banyak gerak.
Aku dan Bos Lan yang pergi.

320
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:48,470
Kau tenang saja.

321
00:16:48,910 --> 00:16:50,720
Kalau Pangeran Mahkota
tak mau bertemu kami,…

322
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:52,280
…aku bakar tempat tinggalnya.

323
00:16:53,230 --> 00:16:55,080
Kau bilang begini, aku semakin
tak tenang.

324
00:16:55,790 --> 00:16:56,780
Kau mengkhawatirkanku?

325
00:16:57,640 --> 00:16:59,030
Aku khawatirkan Putra Mahkota.

326
00:16:59,670 --> 00:17:01,710
Lihat, tak jujur lagi.

327
00:17:02,710 --> 00:17:04,440
Kau tenanglah.
Ada aku yang awasi dia.

328
00:17:04,590 --> 00:17:05,320
Ayo, kita pergi.

329
00:17:05,320 --> 00:17:06,310
Kalian berhati-hatilah.

330
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:08,000
Kalau tidak, antar kau kembali dulu.

331
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:09,950
Begini kau baru bisa
istirahat dengan tenang.

332
00:17:10,520 --> 00:17:11,280
Tak apa.

333
00:17:11,280 --> 00:17:12,190
Aku bisa jalan pelan.

334
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:15,000
Segitiga Besi Emas
saling membantu.

335
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:15,400
Ayo.

336
00:17:15,680 --> 00:17:16,830
Cahaya bulan lumayan.

337
00:17:16,830 --> 00:17:17,680
Aku keluar sebentar.

338
00:17:18,070 --> 00:17:19,900
Langit gelap begini,
ada cahaya bulan apanya?

339
00:17:19,900 --> 00:17:21,040
-Ayo.
-Aku tunggu kau di luar.

340
00:17:21,560 --> 00:17:21,880
Baik.

341
00:17:22,350 --> 00:17:23,560
Hati-hati. Hati-hati sedikit.

342
00:17:23,880 --> 00:17:24,560
Bisa…

343
00:17:25,280 --> 00:17:26,350
Bisa jalan lebih cepat?

344
00:17:26,680 --> 00:17:27,400
Tentu.

345
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:29,640
Lewat sini, lebih dekat.

346
00:17:30,350 --> 00:17:32,040
Kenapa sepertinya lebih jauh?

347
00:17:32,040 --> 00:17:32,430
Tidak.

348
00:17:32,430 --> 00:17:33,000
Kak San.

349
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,070
-Aku rasa panas.
-Tak salah.

350
00:17:34,070 --> 00:17:35,110
Kau haus tidak?

351
00:17:42,350 --> 00:17:43,070
Lihat kau.

352
00:17:43,350 --> 00:17:44,550
Kenapa minum begitu cepat?

353
00:17:45,190 --> 00:17:46,230
Apa kau begitu haus?

354
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:49,830
Bagaimana ini?

355
00:17:50,590 --> 00:17:52,350
Apa Guru dan yang lainnya
bisa tangani?

356
00:17:57,470 --> 00:17:58,190
Rongrong!

357
00:18:01,710 --> 00:18:02,230
Rongrong!

358
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:11,280
Kenapa?

359
00:18:11,330 --> 00:18:13,320
Tadi, aku dan Rongrong
datang untuk lihat kalian.

360
00:18:13,320 --> 00:18:14,280
Namun, dia diculik.

361
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:16,010
Sekarang, Kepala Akademi
sedang kejar.

362
00:18:16,010 --> 00:18:17,160
Diculik? Oleh siapa?

363
00:18:17,430 --> 00:18:18,400
Gerakan orang itu cepat.

364
00:18:18,400 --> 00:18:19,360
Tak bisa lihat jelas.

365
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,560
Dia lari ke mana?

366
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:21,160
Ke sana.

367
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:22,160
Tadi, suara apa?

368
00:18:22,400 --> 00:18:23,400
Rongrong diculik.

369
00:18:24,070 --> 00:18:25,000
Diculik siapa?

370
00:18:25,470 --> 00:18:26,560
Siapa diculik?

371
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,160
Kalian tadi berteriak begitu besar.

372
00:18:31,160 --> 00:18:32,350
Ada apa?

373
00:18:33,400 --> 00:18:34,920
Rongrong diculik.

374
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:36,680
Rongrong dicu…

375
00:18:38,040 --> 00:18:38,920
Rongrong!

376
00:18:43,310 --> 00:18:44,300
Jangan ada yang gerak.

377
00:19:02,710 --> 00:19:04,520
Guru, tak apa?

378
00:19:04,590 --> 00:19:06,890
Pedang yang mengarah padamu itu
adalah teknik roh?

379
00:19:07,350 --> 00:19:10,310
Roh pelindung berupa senjata dengan
kekuatan mengejutkan.

380
00:19:11,230 --> 00:19:13,190
Lawan jauh lebih kuat
dibandingkan kita.

381
00:19:13,880 --> 00:19:15,400
Bukan Master Dunia Douluo lagi, 'kan?

382
00:19:15,430 --> 00:19:16,070
Harusnya, bukan.

383
00:19:16,100 --> 00:19:18,400
Master Dunia Douluo dengan
roh pelindung pedang adalah…

384
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:19,590
…orang Sekte Cahaya Qibao.

385
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:21,230
Tak ada alasan culik Rongrong.

386
00:19:22,760 --> 00:19:24,110
Sekte Cahaya Qibao?

387
00:19:26,280 --> 00:19:28,310
Orang Sekte Cahaya Qibao.

388
00:19:30,070 --> 00:19:31,000
Lepaskan aku!

389
00:19:31,310 --> 00:19:32,710
Apa kau tahu aku siapa?

390
00:19:33,190 --> 00:19:34,430
Siapa kau?!

391
00:19:34,430 --> 00:19:35,920
-Orang jahat!
-Jangan pukul lagi!

392
00:19:35,920 --> 00:19:36,430
Kupukul kau!

393
00:19:36,430 --> 00:19:36,880
Sudah!

394
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:37,880
Pukul! Pukul!

395
00:19:39,000 --> 00:19:39,760
Sudah!

396
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:43,640
Kakek Pedang?

397
00:19:45,830 --> 00:19:47,470
Bocah ini, tega sekali!

398
00:19:47,710 --> 00:19:48,430
Sakit sekali.

399
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:51,400
Untuk apa menculikku?

400
00:19:52,110 --> 00:19:52,710
Sini.

401
00:19:52,710 --> 00:19:53,950
Kepala Akademi, kenapa?

402
00:19:54,230 --> 00:19:54,920
Sini.

403
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:55,950
Duduk, duduk.

404
00:19:56,020 --> 00:19:58,040
Kepala Akademi, kenapa kau
bawa kami kemari?

405
00:19:58,190 --> 00:19:59,490
Semua sedang cari Rongrong.

406
00:19:59,520 --> 00:19:59,920
Benar.

407
00:19:59,920 --> 00:20:02,110
Aku sudah beri tahu
Master dan Erlong.

408
00:20:02,470 --> 00:20:05,590
Biar mereka beri tahu orang Sekte
Cahaya Qibao di cabang Kota Tiandou.

409
00:20:06,070 --> 00:20:08,520
Lagi pula, Sekte Cahaya Qibao
adalah tiga sekte teratas.

410
00:20:08,760 --> 00:20:09,520
Muridnya banyak.

411
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:12,920
Kuharap mereka bisa
cari solusi untuk hal ini.

412
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:15,500
Kalau begitu, kita lebih
harus cari bersama.

413
00:20:16,190 --> 00:20:16,590
Benar.

414
00:20:17,230 --> 00:20:18,070
Jangan panik dulu.

415
00:20:19,190 --> 00:20:20,160
Kalian ada tugas lain.

416
00:20:21,190 --> 00:20:21,710
Tugas?

417
00:20:22,880 --> 00:20:23,800
Tugas apa?

418
00:20:26,070 --> 00:20:26,640
Ini…

419
00:20:28,280 --> 00:20:30,550
…adalah sertifikat perkumpulan
lelang Kota Tiandou.

420
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:32,430
Perkumpulan Lelang?

421
00:20:32,520 --> 00:20:33,640
Aku tadi dapatkan laporan.

422
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:36,560
Pelelangan dimulai besok pagi.

423
00:20:36,830 --> 00:20:38,980
Tanaman obat bermutu
sudah kuajukan untuk dilelang.

424
00:20:39,520 --> 00:20:40,400
Kalian bersiap pergi.

425
00:20:41,350 --> 00:20:43,110
Dengan sertifikat ini
ambil hasilnya.

426
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:45,950
Aku rasa kita masih sempat daftar.

427
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:47,470
Kita bertindak berpisah.

428
00:20:48,640 --> 00:20:49,520
Namun, Kepala Akademi.

429
00:20:50,190 --> 00:20:50,710
Tang San.

430
00:20:51,040 --> 00:20:52,040
Kau teliti.

431
00:20:52,640 --> 00:20:54,800
Xiao Wu juga mengerti
efek tanaman obat.

432
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:57,680
Tugas ini hanya bisa diberikan
pada kalian baru aku bisa tenang.

433
00:20:59,350 --> 00:21:00,830
Lalu, bagaimana dengan Rongrong?

434
00:21:02,350 --> 00:21:03,070
Kau tenang saja.

435
00:21:03,350 --> 00:21:04,740
Kita pasti bisa temukan Rongrong.

436
00:21:05,280 --> 00:21:06,520
Lalu, ikuti lomba bersama.

437
00:21:10,470 --> 00:21:12,680
Jadi, hal ini bukan masalah kecil.

438
00:21:13,190 --> 00:21:13,930
Apa kau mengerti?

439
00:21:13,930 --> 00:21:15,710
Aku tak mengerti!

440
00:21:16,110 --> 00:21:17,810
Kau sebenarnya bawa aku
kemari untuk apa?

441
00:21:17,810 --> 00:21:19,690
-Rongrong.
-Segera bawa aku ke Shi Lanke!

442
00:21:19,690 --> 00:21:21,560
Kau dengarkan saran Kakek,
bisa tidak?

443
00:21:22,520 --> 00:21:23,400
Rongrong!

444
00:21:24,800 --> 00:21:26,260
-Teman seperguruanmu, ya?
-Rongrong!

445
00:21:26,590 --> 00:21:27,430
Mereka mencariku.

446
00:21:27,430 --> 00:21:28,390
Aku sudah harus kembali.

447
00:21:28,390 --> 00:21:29,000
Rongrong.

448
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:29,520
Tak bisa.

449
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:30,950
Intinya, kita temui Ketua Sekte dulu.

450
00:21:30,950 --> 00:21:32,560
Hal lain, dia yang beri tahu kau.

451
00:21:36,760 --> 00:21:37,920
Guru Shi Lanke sempat datang.

452
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:39,000
Katanya, Nona hilang.

453
00:21:39,190 --> 00:21:40,190
Minta kita bantu cari.

454
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,760
Suruh orang berpura-pura.

455
00:21:42,920 --> 00:21:43,840
Jangan sampai bocor.

456
00:21:44,110 --> 00:21:44,470
Baik.

457
00:21:46,000 --> 00:21:48,000
Kenapa tak perbolehkan
aku kembali ke akademi?

458
00:21:48,230 --> 00:21:50,040
Baik-baik saja.
Kenapa bawa aku ke sekte?

459
00:21:50,590 --> 00:21:52,400
Ini niat Ketua Sekte.

460
00:21:52,400 --> 00:21:53,070
Tak mungkin.

461
00:21:53,560 --> 00:21:56,560
Awal aku pergi ke Shi Lanke
karena disuruh Ayah.

462
00:21:56,680 --> 00:21:57,560
Bagaimana mungkin…

463
00:22:02,560 --> 00:22:03,280
Kakek Pedang.

464
00:22:03,830 --> 00:22:05,070
Apakah sekte kacau?

465
00:22:05,070 --> 00:22:11,350
Kau sebagai salah satu tetua
menculikku dan jadikan aku sandera?

466
00:22:11,350 --> 00:22:12,830
Kau pikir dari mana?

467
00:22:12,830 --> 00:22:13,880
Apa-apaan ini?

468
00:22:14,000 --> 00:22:16,110
Kalau bukan begitu,
maka jelaskan padaku!

469
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:17,470
Hal ini…

470
00:22:17,470 --> 00:22:18,230
Ini niatku.

